{"tid":379148,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"晚上出戰金牌戰 日本隊全隊早上去幫手打掃公園","createTime":"2017-08-29T05:11:59.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-29T05:16:55.000Z","uid":31314,"like":4,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"f2d1af71b57c22081f27dc2729abbcbd8d1d3170","tid":379148,"uid":31314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-29T05:11:59.000Z","msg":"中國國民黨籍新北市議員蔡淑君今天表示，世界大學運動會日本選手自發到<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>新北市</strong></span>林口區社區運動公園整理環境，覺得「很棒」；網友也留言，「好感人的民族性，值得我們借鏡」。<br />\n<br />\n蔡淑君上午在社群網站臉書（facebook）貼出3張照片表示：「外國選手們，現拿著掃把畚箕，自發性到林口社區運動公園整理環境。」<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">不少網友認出是日本隊</span>，表達感謝及感動。網友紛紛表示：「好感動！真的是運動家的精神值得我們學習」、還有網友說：「這樣才是的真正的國民外交，好感度整個爆表。」<br />\n<br />\n有網友說，台灣第一次辦如此大規模賽事，選手們主動為台灣保護環境，希望全國民眾不要再隨地亂丟垃圾，給這些選手大力按讚。<br />\n<img src=\"https://ir0.mobify.com/500/http://attach.setn.com/newsimages/2017/08/29/1031767-XXL.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fir0.mobify.com%2F500%2Fhttp%3A%2F%2Fattach.setn.com%2Fnewsimages%2F2017%2F08%2F29%2F1031767-XXL.jpg&h=a0c5f657&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://ir0.mobify.com/500/http://attach.setn.com/newsimages/2017/08/29/1031764-XXL.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fir0.mobify.com%2F500%2Fhttp%3A%2F%2Fattach.setn.com%2Fnewsimages%2F2017%2F08%2F29%2F1031764-XXL.jpg&h=d75b24a7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://ir0.mobify.com/500/http://attach.setn.com/newsimages/2017/08/29/1031765-XXL.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fir0.mobify.com%2F500%2Fhttp%3A%2F%2Fattach.setn.com%2Fnewsimages%2F2017%2F08%2F29%2F1031765-XXL.jpg&h=4cfe68c8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n新北市+1分<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/lomore_shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/lomore_shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/lomore_shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"00db8c86512827c1b7de99c627909bf6f430985b","tid":379148,"uid":35430,"like":0,